    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386370/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1753880180\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386370/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1753880180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386370/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1753880180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Last Life是一款令人激动的冒险游戏，故事发生在名为NeoNova的赛博朋克城市，融合了高科技和黑暗的秘密。我们的主人公将作为一只可爱的猫由玩家操控，踏上一段神秘的旅程，寻找失踪的爱人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386370/extras/4501efd989fca9e6be29a80424bc4535.poster.avif?t=1753880180\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386370/extras/4501efd989fca9e6be29a80424bc4535.webm?t=1753880180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386370/extras/4501efd989fca9e6be29a80424bc4535.mp4?t=1753880180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在游戏中，我们的猫和爱人生活在一个人工实验森林中。然而，有一天，爱人突然消失了，我们的猫逃离实验森林，踏上了NeoNova之旅。这个令人惊叹、充满霓虹灯的城市充满了神秘的居民、危险区域和复杂的谜题。<br><br>猫的任务是在NeoNova复杂的街道中徘徊，寻找爱人的踪迹并拯救她。沿途你会遇到不同的角色，收集线索，探索城市的不同区域。你将解决谜题，克服困难，并通过与其他物体和生物互动，深入了解故事的内涵。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386370/extras/76b338001116e5410da231ba98b371fd.poster.avif?t=1753880180\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386370/extras/76b338001116e5410da231ba98b371fd.webm?t=1753880180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386370/extras/76b338001116e5410da231ba98b371fd.mp4?t=1753880180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Last Life: NeoNova街道提供了一个令人惊叹的冒险体验，拥有令人印象深刻的图像风格、激动人心的故事和简单的游戏机制。展现出你作为猫的勇气和智慧，揭示秘密，揭露黑暗的过去，拯救你的爱人。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你准备好了吗？Last Life等待着你！</h2>",
